                     <hi rend="italic">There was another indictment against Muggeridge, for the forgery of the</hi> 50<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. <hi rend="italic">cheque</hi>
                  </rs>
                  <hi rend="italic">, <rs id="t18750816-454-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
